title: Four new isocoumarins from Cajanus cajan
content:
RSC Adv., 2024, 14,7763-7769
DOI: 10.1039/D3RA08149D, Paper
Open Access

Liyuan Yao, Aikebaier Jumai, Xiaobao Huang, Tingting Lin, Zhengguo Tao, Sheng-Xiang Qiu
Four novel new isocoumarins, cajanolactone B, C, D1 and D2 (1–4), were isolated from ethanolic extracts of the leaves of Cajanus cajan.
